NBT Bank Logo NBT Bank, N.A. is an American financial institution that operates through a network of more than 150 banking locations serving north-eastern states including offices in New York, Pennsylvania, Vermont, Massachusetts, New Hampshire and Maine. NBT Bank and its parent company, NBT Bancorp Inc., are headquartered in Norwich, New York, United States. NBT Bancorp is traded on the Nasdaq Global Select Market under the symbol NBTB. Source
